title: Fortios: SSLVPN
agents: special
catalog: network/fortigate
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the SSL VPN Service of a Fortigate firewall.
 The number of active SSL VPN sessions is monitored.
 It also displays 
 which users are connected and how many tunnels are open.
 The bandwidth used is monitored.

 The check is always displayed as {ok}.

 The special agent is required for this check, 
 which can be configured via “FortiOS”.

discovery:
 One service is created.
